data.description: HOME FOR THE HOLIDAYS in this 4 Bdrm/3.5 bath home in quiet Prairie Creek Neighborhood w/in walking distance to the Elementary & Intermediate Schools. Open concept floor plan offers great flow & great natural light. Open to Living/Dining areas, the kitchen has great cabinet/counter space, SS appliances, granite breakfast bar & large pantry. It's a cook's delight! Entertain in front of the cozy gas fireplace in the Living Rm or curl up for movie night in the spacious LL Family Rm w/ space for craft/play area or home office. The Primary Bdrm & Laundry are on main floor, making this is a great option for aging in place: spend many years here making memories! Upstairs: 2 Bdrms, full bath & study nook. LL hosts 4th Bdrm, Fmly Rm & 3rd full bath. Plus great storage, large yard & spacious garage.
